            <p class="comment-content">图片不错。文字不是我好的那口。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="513266236">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-513266236" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-513266236" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="513266236">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/XYST4XDUSTB/">小尘4x</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2012-08-21</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">《另一种讲述的方式》引用大量例子 看似好懂 实际上晦涩性与桑塔格的《论摄影》不相伯仲  如果说成为摄影家必读四人是 约翰伯格 桑塔格 罗兰巴特和本雅明 那我已经读过两个人了</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="50111783">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-50111783" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-50111783" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="50111783">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/irissong/">若梦</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar30 rating" title="还行"></span>
